A weathered wooden café table in golden afternoon light, steam rising from a ceramic cup of coffee, across from it sits an elderly Indian man in simple white robes with a serene expression, his hands gesturing mid-conversation, the background showing a soft-focus Bangkok street scene with golden temple spires visible through large windows, warm amber and saffron tones dominating the palette, photorealistic style with shallow depth of field focusing on the steam and the holy man's expressive hands, capturing a moment of unexpected spiritual connection in an everyday urban setting.
